<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8f14f445-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s1642i"><num value="1642i">§ 1642i.</num><heading> Certification of awards</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission shall certify to the Secretary of the Treasury, in terms of United States currency, each award made pursuant to this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8f14f446-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/act/1950-03-10/ch54">Mar. 10, 1950, ch. 54</ref>, title IV, § 410, as added <ref href="/us/pl/85/604/s1">Pub. L. 85–604, § 1</ref>, <date date="1958-08-08">Aug. 8, 1958</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/72/529">72 Stat. 529</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
